@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>This weather application respects your privacy. We do not store any personal information beyond your search history, which is stored locally in your browser session and is automatically cleared when you close your browser.</p>

<h3>Data Collection</h3>
<p>We only collect the city names you search for to provide weather information. This data is stored temporarily in your browser session and is not transmitted to any external servers except for the weather API requests.</p>

<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
<p>This application uses the OpenWeatherMap API to fetch weather data. Please refer to their privacy policy for information about how they handle data.</p>

<h3>Contact</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us.</p>
